{"tid":818400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"花槽突然跳出條蜥蜴 街坊怕怕","createTime":"2018-09-14T05:33:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T06:43:50.000Z","uid":122,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d28bc525ab564d040084cb4a70be07bd64e1dd23","tid":818400,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T05:33:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180914/large/1536900382_f461.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180914%2Flarge%2F1536900382_f461.jpg&h=27c6c193&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n慈雲山慈愛苑出現不速之客！早上10時半，有居民發現，愛寧閣地下花槽有一隻約一呢長的蜥蜴，大驚下報警。該隻蜥蜴青綠色，翹首以待，伏在地上四處張望。警員到場圍封花槽，召愛護動物協會到場跟進。"},{"pid":"6e4a7416ad6552e18bf60153ea1be8beb421b80a","tid":818400,"uid":95,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T05:34:30.000Z","msg":"小小野都驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e99bb6b5b98455cb51817383a5e3eb3b518f3279","tid":818400,"uid":122,"like":42,"dislike":2,"score":40,"quote":{"pid":"6e4a7416ad6552e18bf60153ea1be8beb421b80a","tid":818400,"uid":95,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T05:34:30.000Z","msg":"小小野都驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T05:35:45.000Z","msg":"斬豬肉聲嚇親 細膽師奶報警<br />\n<br />\n一名膽小婦人，下午 2時 20分，到沙田隆亨街市買，當她走到肉檔對開時，疑被肉檔職員手起刀落的斬豬肉聲嚇倒，婦人嚇破膽，受驚之下致電報警，事後由救護車送院治理。 <br />\n<br />\n一名膽小婦人，到沙田隆亨街市買時，報稱被肉檔斬豬肉聲音嚇倒。"},{"pid":"11622f6f10d84b6a434d943eb139850326a2257a","tid":818400,"uid":95,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e99bb6b5b98455cb51817383a5e3eb3b518f3279","tid":818400,"uid":122,"like":42,"dislike":2,"score":40,"quote":{"pid":"6e4a7416ad6552e18bf60153ea1be8beb421b80a","tid":818400,"uid":95,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T05:34:30.000Z","msg":"小小野都驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cite